Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing is endless as the everlasting sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani hitotsu te ni todokanai yōna
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing out there that is out of my reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hi no biru no sukima kara mieta gaitō ni
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Tonight's streetlights in between buildings sites\NAre too bright on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,5,,Watashi ga nanimonona no ka tte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For so long I \NDidn't know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,5,,Utau koto wa nanina no katte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}What songs I sing \NAnd what songs I sang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hito ha ai o kuretakatte shiritaku mo nai
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For long enough that the one offering love \NDoesn't want to know me now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo itamunara kono itaminara
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But even if you're getting hurt, \NEven if it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,5,,Mōsukoshi mōsukoshi itai gurai ga ī
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}In a little more, just a little more\NThis pain will turn to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,5,,Kirainara kirai to ima kotoba ni shite
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Say you hate me, say all you want\NYour words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,5,,Mienai ashita o koko de owara sete
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo an'nani aishita kon'nani aishiteru
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But how I loved you before,\NI love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,600)}Sono shiawase no hitotsude ī oboete ite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,600)}And how sincerely happy we were in old days\NI will never forget
Comment: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{OP ED border}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of tending to us and our family, \Ndad preferred to design pachislot machines?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:01:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a thing... Such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:03.55,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(800,700)\an8\c&HFBFDFE&\bord1\shad2\blur2\3c&H5C54BE&\4c&H2E36B1&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs45\4a&H00&\fscx117\fscy88}Episode 11\N {\fs90}Days Gone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since the match started, \Nthis guy have not stopped once in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take him just 5 more to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We have seen his games before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... Shit, shit! Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded. \NThe winner is Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Note, that the current Otonashi's victory \Nin just 35 minutes has set a new record for Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The game is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dealer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My heartfelt congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what a bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That felt like one hell of a weird game, \Neven though I inadvertently won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen what just happened? \NHow I fought?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, you'll be getting \Na challenge from me in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overvaluing me. \NI'm not to remain the Ultimate King for the eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go on pressing buttons this way, no matter how many times you challenge me, it is all in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being the usual you, \Npressing buttons with anger and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural, you had no trouble \Nseeing through my heart's mood once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But can it be due to you \Npressing the buttons with hatred as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know pachislot allegedly killed your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough to hate pachislot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pray that you \Ndo not lose your next game as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come back to vex me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really vex you that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Yuri? \NDoing deliveries?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. \NDoing pachislot with Oumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With Oumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi kept obstinately vexing her with invitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cafes, leisures... \NWell, all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But recently, Yuri embraced pachislot, \Nrefusing to accept his courting any other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Master, can I still vex you with a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! \NThose two's rapprochement {\i1}does{\i0} bother you after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing! That's not what I wanted to ask. \NTell me about Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,From what you know of Daiba, \Nwhat kind of person he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I knew what kind of person he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't have any idea \Nwhat was this guy before coming to Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if only a smidgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it \Nhow come he doesn't hate pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it looked like at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Daiba's deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When he first appeared at Slothium, \Nit was like he is fighting a swordfight. That's what I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have my brand one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as I abandoned my hatred, \NI could see the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, we're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to forgive us. \NYuri's self-indulgence carried her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is special. So, how did it go? \NWere you victorious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Winner, winner, chicken dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, Yuri has everything it takes \Nto become a first-class slotter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally came, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pachislot addiction is getting out of hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so ablaze about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing of the kind. \NI'm not ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Ginya can't stand the sight \Nof me and Yuri finally having a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not allowed to enjoy pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it only allowed for Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Yuri, I am not playing it for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, you do not enjoy pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You press the buttons with anger and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I do... I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, are you experiencing a slump?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, people say novelists have periods of slump \Nsometimes, when they can't write a line,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,be it even a mere article.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And with Ginya's miniscule brain, \Nslump is only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you call miniscule-brained?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be ashamed of. \NIt can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be mitigated \Nby going shopping with me tomorrow though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To carry my bags around, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will happily join you for a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good to go on dates every day. \NHow about you go to work for a change, Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, we're good to go. \NIt's decided then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I'll do the dishwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you have to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After his best friend's death, \Nwhat became of this Daiba guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had any idea myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All I've heard was \Nthat weird Double Pachislot-Suicide rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There {\i1}should{\i0} be something else concerning Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, unless he coped with his hate for pachislot. \NBut was it really possible in his position?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you meet Daiba somewhere recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiding the sensation. \NGinya, you are almost a real reporter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about Daiba, \Nbut I can remember one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,People say he was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When Daiba first saw Fushina dead, \NFushina's face is said to have been grinning blissfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you inquire \Nin the Toto University yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good chance you stumble upon someone \Nwho was attending the same class as Fushina and Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! \NThank you, Ms. Ishibashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one excited departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All the tea stalks are standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here again, Fushina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.34,Song,,0,0,0,,Faculty of Electronic Engineering
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you that reporter for the magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is me. Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's you, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you want to hear about, then? \NThe new negative resistance superconductor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it the chemistry \Nof organometallic vapor deposition?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that is troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't bother to study the subject \Nprior to the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't waste my experiment time on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, gonna get back to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute more, \NProfessor Umeyashiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a Professor, but the Assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Can Professor Assistant Umeyashiki \Ntell me about times of his studentship here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when he was a classmate \Nof Mr. Daiba Ryo and Mr. Fushina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba? Fushina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Those names bring back so much memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If those two were still here, \Nboth would have already become professors by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you saying they were both {\i1}that{\i0} excellent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba and Fushina were two geniuses, \Nequally eligible to be the faculty's number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They were rivals, \Nbut also best friends at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be trying my best studying \Nand still remain below their ground zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They were often helping me out studying. \NYes, I remember that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In various kinds of the recoil response,\Nthe electrons wavelengths arrange by layer thickness
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and come into superposition \Nin the artificial crystals of superlattice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daiba, are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands are full, open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that you, Fushina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The pachislot gainings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't eat it all by myself, so treat yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all from pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I solved your supper problem for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having an exam coming. \NSure you want to spend every day playing pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I also snatched Daiba's favorite cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Our preparedness renders it already over. \NThus, until the exam day, I have nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Geniuses can omit preparing for exams?\NWish I could someday say such a line on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad that genius is only passionate about one thing. \NIs pachislot really that exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It may seem primitive at first glance, \Nbut on the inside, pachislot really is rich and in-depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All it takes is just some spinning titles \Nand a bit of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It even has its own philosophy. \NIn a way, it gives me the religious vibes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With time, I will certainly unravel \Nthe essence of pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overdramatizing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try and see for yourself. \NEither way, pachislot is a whole lot of fun, Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you're not enjoying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we haven't seen him for a while. \NWe found out Fushina bought a pachislot machine though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fushina! You have not been coming to university lately. \NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more. \NI will show you everything just a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last time I saw Fushina alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,His death was a shock to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after, Daiba transformed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Transformed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped attending the university, \Nspending his days in the parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A gossip sprout at that time, \Nthat he destroyed god knows how many stores on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:31.11,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(900,800)}Dear customers, we appreciate your lasting fidelity. \NAfter a long break, our store will be reopened on the 10th of this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, Daiba went...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's about as much as I can tell.\NI don't have any idea what happened after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fushina,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated pachislot, \Nvowed to take my revenge on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I found out about Slothium, \NI entered without a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in, Fushina!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you align!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This game's outsider Daiba Ryo \Nhas lost his privilege to fight for a Knight's title.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Fushina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I will ever succeed in avenging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You should enjoy it, Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you play with hatred, \Nyou cannot unravel the essence of pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Try enjoying it, more. \NPachislot is a whole lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fushina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have always wanted to see it \Nthe way you saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But alas, it does not seem I have much more time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why \NI must do whatever is still in my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way I felt when I was young. \NI hated pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, up to carrying some bags today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me and don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember what you taught me once, \Nand I know, I should convey it to him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? \NYou know it's a parlor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the shopping part?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get everything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to accompany me, remember? \NCome on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you afraid of?\NGo ahead and teach me to adjust my eyes to the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Mister Ginya Windmill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's begin with the basics. \NFirst, try to aim for that red flashy Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Here I go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a simple Small Factor. \NGuess that overreaction cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, how do I aim for the Big now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't call it aiming...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is rather a matter of luck. \NWhen you play, you kinda do a lottery draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The machines usually have \Nfrom 1 to 6 settings for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But even the most lavish setting for this machine \Nhas a chance of just 240 to 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I have to play no less than 240 times?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I said \Nit's a lottery draw inside the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, a pro and a rookie have the same chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, this one is a secured forerunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! \NGinya, it's a Big. A Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, try not to miss the Small Factor. \NYou grasped the timings from earlier, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, you seem to be really enjoying it to the full.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when Daiba appeared at his third game, \Nhis eyes were completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no way of knowing what caused that change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that fella?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he give up before fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba's face was never the same since that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,His way of pressing pachislot buttons was joy-fueled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, I have never seen such a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That pattern seems somehow odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Yuri, that's another secured forerunner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! It's a consecutive hit, a Renchan! \NGinya, V!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have won a lot. A lot! \NHey, do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I suddenly become so keen about pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... \NBecause you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought I became so keen about pachislot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to cognize Ginya's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to understand how Ginya feels about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I personally enjoy it, \Nfor Ginya it's a whole other thing, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since he started playing pachislot, \NGinya changed completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He became anxious, sorrowful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seemingly oblivious to very concept of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If it goes on this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels like Ginya would only stray further away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. \NAnd sorry for borrowing you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was still fun. \NSpending a day with Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Time left: 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... Am I going to keep on losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:05.40,0:20:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,600)}With hatred alone, you can't win in pachislot.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(600,600)}Ginya, you don't enjoy pachislot at all?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:09.04,0:20:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(600,600)}When Daiba first found Fushina dead, \NFushina was said to have been smiling.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.94,0:20:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(600,600)}I have never seen someone pressing pachislot buttons \Nwith such a joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(600,600)}At this rate, Ginya will probably \Nend up somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of my father, \NI have a life of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, here and now, \NI must conquer my own place in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not going anywhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have regained your composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After throwing away the hatred, \Nyou saw the light.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.69,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.71,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.69,0:21:34.27,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}My youth goes on, pushing me in my back with no rest,\NAnd the scarlet sky will soon start pouring water again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:34.29,Song,,0,0,5,,Seishun ga boku no senaka o oshite akai sora utsuru mizutamari
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.27,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}With my leg in a clutch, suddenly the sky shivered, \NSo unawares, making such stupid look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,5,,Ashimoto ga tora rete ite sora wa ureru bakaridatta
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,5,,Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.22,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.21,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,800)}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,800)}Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: \NBonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will \Nstop the time.
